---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Nick Gray Case Study | Dino Favara Jr."
  description="Took average views from 7,288 to 1.5M total views in 90 days. And drove measurable book sales."
>
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <!-- Back link -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10">
      <a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary/70 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
        &larr; All case studies
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-700 tracking-wide mb-6">
        Brand Growth + Revenue
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-dark mb-4">
        Nick Gray
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg font-light text-dark/60 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Took average views from 7,288 to 1.5M total views in 90 days. And drove measurable book sales.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
        {['TikTok Strategy', 'Content System Design', 'Format Development', 'Book Launch Support'].map(tag => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-dark/10 bg-white/60 text-xs font-medium text-dark/55">
            {tag}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Before / After -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/70 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr]">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Avg Views Before</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-red-500">7,288</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">per video</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center px-4">
            <span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&rarr;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex md:hidden items-center justify-center py-2">
            <span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&darr;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center bg-amber-500/4">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Total Views After</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-amber-600">1.54M</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">in 90 days</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Metrics Grid -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {[
          { value: '10.8K', label: 'TikTok Followers', sub: '(from 6,052)' },
          { value: '124.1K', label: 'Total Likes', sub: '' },
          { value: '477.9K', label: 'Top Video Views', sub: '' },
          { value: '10 → 17', label: 'Daily Book Sales', sub: '' },
        ].map(m => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-5 text-center">
            <span class="font-display text-2xl text-amber-600">{m.value}</span>
            <p class="mt-1 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/45">{m.label}</p>
            {m.sub && <p class="mt-0.5 text-[10px] text-dark/35">{m.sub}</p>}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Body Content -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
      <article class="prose-custom">
        <h3>The Situation</h3>
        <p>Nick Gray is the author of <em>The 2-Hour Cocktail Party</em> and a well-known figure in the networking and event space. He had a TikTok presence with around 6,000 followers, but his content was inconsistent. It was a mix of party tips, food reviews, book promotion, and random vlogs. There was no clear content thesis or repeatable format. Average views sat around 7,288 per video.</p>

        <h3>The Approach</h3>
        <p>I rebuilt Nick's content strategy around a single thesis: <strong>Nick is the king of party planning, and every video should reinforce that identity.</strong> We developed a pinned video strategy, created recurring formats tied to his book and party expertise, and built a content calendar that balanced personality-driven content with discoverable, format-driven posts.</p>
        <p>Key formats included party formula explainers, "who to invite" advice, event BTS, and the "Met Museum Secrets" series that showcased Nick's natural curiosity in a way that still felt on-brand. We also optimized his bio, pinned videos, and call-to-action flow to drive traffic to his book.</p>

        <h3>The Results</h3>
        <p>In 90 days, Nick generated 1,541,670 total views. His followers grew from 6,052 to 10,800, a 78% increase. His total likes jumped from 29.3K to 124.1K. Individual videos hit 100K+ views, with one reaching 477.9K.</p>
        <p>The revenue impact was the real win. Nick reported that a single video drove more book page views than anything prior — approximately 50 clicks on his profile link and a measurable bump in daily book sales from an average of 10 to 17 per day.</p>

        <blockquote>
          <p>"When I posted a video, it goes 2k views. But Mercury Media helped in tweaking the video and it got over 100k+ views!"</p>
          <cite>Nick Gray, Author of The 2-Hour Cocktail Party</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-dark/8">
        <span class="text-sm font-light text-dark/45">Timeline: 90 days</span>
        <div class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-full rounded-full bg-dark/6 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-primary" style="width: 50%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-xl text-dark">Want results like this?</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-light text-dark/55 mt-1">Let's talk about building your content engine.</p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="mailto:dino@mercurysocialmedia.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-primary text-off-white font-medium text-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95 whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          Email me &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-custom h3 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--dark); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose-custom h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose-custom p { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.65); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .prose-custom strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--dark); }
  .prose-custom em { font-style: italic; }
  .prose-custom blockquote { border-left: 3px solid var(--primary); padding: 1rem 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; background: rgba(107, 92, 231, 0.04); border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0; }
  .prose-custom blockquote p { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prose-custom blockquote cite { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.45); }
</style>
